<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.185992>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Female antennal flagellomere 4, lateral view (A, B), male maxillary palp, dorsal view (C), male (D) and female (E) wing, dorsal view, and apical part of female abdomen, lateral view (G, F). A, C, D, F: Manota avita sp. n. (from Doi Inthanon NP, D and C paratypes). B, E, G: M. collina Hippa (from Doi Inthanon NP). Scale for A and B 0.05 mm, for C, F and G 0.1 mm and for D and E 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/185992/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.185993>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Manota avita sp. n. (holotype): A. Antennal flagellomere 4, lateral view. B. Hypopygium, dorsal view. C. Mesial structures of gonocoxa, ventral view. D. Hypopygium, ventral view. Scale 0.10 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/185993/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

